Title: Business intelligence for physical examination platform service reporting system

Abstract: Currently, the capability to present reports or data accurately, fast and insightfully is highly required for the company to make data-driven decision. This paper is intended to solve the problem in one company which serves more than sixteen professional companies in South East Asia area. This report is useful to make decisions in this company. The method chosen to develop the data warehouse along with its analytics and reports is Kimball methodology which has been introduced since the mid-1980s and has been used by a lot of prior researchers. As the data can be displayed in various form as it needed, the stakeholder can make the data-driven decision which benefits this company to perform better in the market. © 2017 IEEE.
